tip.text: We had the signature burger set and it was so filling. Patty feels more solid than Carl's Jr and tastes better! Couldn't even have a second serving of free-flow soup, I was so full.
The Vietnamese pork chop with broken rice and BBQ Chicken noodle salad were SO GOOD! Can't wait to return to try other items on their menu.
A lot more trees and shade than the rest of Changi Beach. Great discovery today. Shall come here more often.
The zhui kway is tremendously good. There's always a line especially on Sundays and public holidays like National Day. Ask to separate the gravy sauce if you're eating it later. Stays fresh that way.
The Shiok maki really has to be tasted to be believed. A bit pricey but I've really never tasted any maki like this!
